org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.scheduler.fair.allocation

Class QueueProperties.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.scheduler.fair.allocation.QueueProperties.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    QueueProperties

    public static final class QueueProperties.Builder
extends Object
    Builder class for QueueProperties. All methods are adding queue properties to the maps of this builder keyed by the queue's name except some methods like isAclDefinedForAccessType(String, AccessType) or getMinQueueResources().
